---
const currentYear = new Date().getFullYear();
---

<footer class="bg-surface-variant dark:bg-dark-surface-variant pt-16 pb-8 border-t border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-800 transition-colors duration-300">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-4 gap-12 mb-12">
      <!-- Brand -->
      <div class="col-span-1 md:col-span-2">
        <a href="/" class="flex items-center gap-2 group mb-4">
          <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-primary flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold text-lg">
            A
          </div>
          <span class="text-xl font-bold tracking-tight text-on-surface dark:text-dark-on-surface">
            Arce<span class="text-primary">Apps</span>
          </span>
        </a>
        <p class="text-on-surface-variant dark:text-dark-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed max-w-sm">
          Desarrollando experiencias móviles únicas. Aplicaciones diseñadas con pasión, enfoque en el usuario y los más altos estándares de calidad.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Links -->
      <div>
        <h3 class="font-bold text-on-surface dark:text-dark-on-surface mb-4">Navegación</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-3">
          <li><a href="/" class="text-on-surface-variant dark:text-dark-on-surface-variant hover:text-primary transition-colors">Inicio</a></li>
          <li><a href="/#apps" class="text-on-surface-variant dark:text-dark-on-surface-variant hover:text-primary transition-colors">Aplicaciones</a></li>
          <li><a href="/blog" class="text-on-surface-variant dark:text-dark-on-surface-variant hover:text-primary transition-colors">Blog</a></li>
          <li><a href="/about" class="text-on-surface-variant dark:text-dark-on-surface-variant hover:text-primary transition-colors">Sobre Mí</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- Legal & Social -->
      <div>
        <h3 class="font-bold text-on-surface dark:text-dark-on-surface mb-4">Legal</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-3">
          <li><a href="/politica-privacidad" class="text-on-surface-variant dark:text-dark-on-surface-variant hover:text-primary transition-colors">Política de Privacidad</a></li>
          <li><a href="/privacy-policy" class="text-on-surface-variant dark:text-dark-on-surface-variant hover:text-primary transition-colors">Privacy Policy (EN)</a></li>
        </ul>

        <div class="mt-6 flex gap-4">
            <!-- Google Play Icon -->
            <a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/developer?id=Arce+Apps" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-on-surface-variant dark:text-dark-on-surface-variant hover:text-primary transition-colors" aria-label="Google Play">
                <span class="material-icons">shop</span>
            </a>
            <!-- GitHub Icon -->
            <a href="https://github.com/arceapps" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-on-surface-variant dark:text-dark-on-surface-variant hover:text-primary transition-colors" aria-label="GitHub">
                <span class="material-icons">code</span>
            </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="border-t border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-700 pt-8 flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-center gap-4 text-sm text-on-surface-variant/80 dark:text-dark-on-surface-variant/80">
      <p>&copy; {currentYear} ArceApps. Todos los derechos reservados.</p>
      <p>Diseñado con <span class="text-secondary">♥</span> y Material Design.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
